title: To Jacky Dearest
author: NJpalms
pages:
#- My Dearest Jacky,

I most certainly enjoyed my night of silliness and thank you for taking part (and also staying patient with me). 

Hopefully I wasn't too much of a pain :P 


#- I'd be happy to practice the cool PVP with you if you'd like to in the future. Then you can 420XxNOSCOPExXRek people like it aint no thang. 

I did wake up with a headache today but having mail from you greatly improved my
#- morning, so thank you for that as well!

Love, 

- NJ
